embeds.title: How do I use Catwalks/Vactubes/Unstationary Scaffolds?
embeds.description: These items effectively act as nodes, which need to be connected to each other in order to do anything. The exact way in which this works is different for each item, see their wiki pages for more details: [Vactubes](https://github.com/BEEmod/BEE2-items/wiki/Vactubes), [Catwalks](https://github.com/BEEmod/BEE2-items/wiki/Catwalks), and [Unstationary Scaffolds](https://github.com/BEEmod/BEE2-items/wiki/Unstationary-Scaffold)
